<refsynopsisdiv>
   <title>Calling Sequence</title>
   <synopsis>
   line3d(varargin)
   
   </synopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsection>
   <title>Parameters</title>
   <variablelist>
   <varlistentry><term>varargin :</term>
      <listitem><para> if string then it's the line2d 's identity and if matrix then it's line2d 's point coordinates</para></listitem></varlistentry>
   </variablelist>
</refsection>

<refsection>
   <title>Description</title>
   <para>
line2d returns an empty list if varagin is a string or a list that contains :
Id : identity
Coor : coordinates matrix
Seg  : segment matrix
   </para>
   <para>
</para>
</refsection>

